                    "content": "<p><span style=\"color:#696969;\">Wil je nog een keer de uitleg doornemen? Bekijk dan de onderstaande video's.</span></p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9U4WWTifO7M\" width=\"560\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ISo2LL1aO8Y\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" class=\"video-item\"/>"
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><span style=\"color:#696969;\"><strong>Vond je de toets moeilijk of had je meer dan vier fouten, bekijk dan nog even de video's onder het kopje 'extra uitleg'.</strong></span></p>\n"
